---
title: Sweet and Smoky Chipotle Chicken with Charred Veggies and Buttery Rice
description: Juicy, sweet and sticky chicken breast slices adorn cilantro rice in this Tex-Mex inspired bowl. Charred corn and carrots add veggie wholesomeness to an already delicious meal!
